<h1 id="c:categories" class="tex-chapter"><span data-tag="0007">2</span> Algebraic prerequisites: monoidal categories</h1>

<p>
In this chapter we introduce some of the algebraic language necessary for describing TQFTs, most importantly the notion of a monoidal category. We only give a very brief introduction, referring the reader to books <span class="cite">[<a href="/bibliography/mac-lane">ML1998</a>]</span>, <span class="cite">[<a href="/bibliography/etingof-fusion">EGNO2015</a>]</span> for details. 
</p>
